    <div class="main review-item" id="5650697">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5650697/" class="title-link">中国式的坐天下</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5650697"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36330632/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36330632-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36330632/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">meri</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-11-11"
      class="main-meta">2012-11-11 22:02:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5650697_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    天下、江湖是比较独特的两个字，真要给出明确的定义是件不简单的事情。江湖的故事太多了，就不说了，今天说说天下，我百度了一下天下，具体解释为：天下是东亚民族对世界的专有概念。字义上的意思为“普天之下”，没有地理和空间的限制，不过，也有不同的用法，用来形容某一...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5650697/#comments">(8回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5650697_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5650697_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










